programme.desc: Weeks before Christmas, an interior designer is hired to decorate the estate of a wealthy businessman.

programme.title: Falling Like Snowflakes

programme.title: Project Christmas Wish
programme.desc: A womans life becomes transformed as she works toward granting a little girls wish for a Christmas like she used to have with her mother.

programme.desc: A single woman with a newly adopted baby gets stuck in Bethlehem, Pa.; with no room at the inn, shes forced to stay with a stranger who turns out to be the miracle she has needed.

programme.title: Christmas at the Plaza
programme.desc: When historian Jessica is hired to create the Plazas Christmas display, she finds more than facts while teaming up with handsome decorator Nick to bring the display to life.

programme.title: Catch Me if You Claus
programme.desc: Avery Quinns shot at anchoring news clashes with a Santa-suited intruder, Chris, who insists hes Santas son on a first Christmas mission. They unravel a career-making story together.

programme.title: Last Christmas
programme.desc: Nothing seems to go right for young Kate, a frustrated Londoner who works as an elf in a year-round Christmas shop. But things soon take a turn for the better when she develops a growing attraction to a charming suitor who seems too good to be true.

programme.title: The Christmas House
programme.desc: Working through some difficult decisions, a mother and father summon their two grown sons home for the holidays.

programme.title: The Christmas House 2: Deck Those Halls

programme.title: Three Wise Men and a Baby

programme.title: On the 12th Date of Christmas

programme.title: Single and Ready to Jingle

programme.title: Switched for Christmas
